{
  "info": {
    "name": "Vidra Core Edge Cases & Security Tests",
    "description": "Comprehensive edge case and security testing for Vidra Core API\n\n## Test Categories\n\n1. **SSRF Protection** - Server-Side Request Forgery prevention\n2. **Comment Edge Cases** - Comment counting and validation\n3. **Input Validation** - Boundary testing and injection attempts\n4. **Rate Limiting** - Concurrent request handling\n5. **Remote Video Import** - Federation and import security\n\n## Critical Security Tests\n\n- Private IP blocking (192.168.x.x, 10.x.x.x, 172.16.x.x)\n- AWS metadata service protection (169.254.169.254)\n- Localhost variants blocking\n- Protocol validation (HTTPS only)\n- File size limits\n- URL length limits\n- SQL injection attempts\n- XSS payload detection\n\n## Environment Variables\n\n- `baseUrl` - API base URL (e.g., http://localhost:8080)\n- `access_token` - JWT authentication token",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "edge-case-security-tests"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://app-test:8080",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "access_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "test_video_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "['access_token', 'video_id', 'test_video_id'].forEach(function(key) {",
          "  var envVal = pm.environment.get(key);",
          "  if (envVal) {",
          "    pm.collectionVariables.set(key, envVal);",
          "  }",
          "});",
          "var vid = pm.environment.get('video_id');",
          "if (vid) {",
          "  pm.collectionVariables.set('test_video_id', vid);",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "01 - SSRF Protection Tests",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Block Private IP 192.168.x.x",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "    pm.expect([400, 403, 404, 500]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "if (pm.response.code >= 200 && pm.response.code < 300) {",
                  "  pm.test('Should reject private IP range 192.168.x.x', () => {",
                  "  });",
                  "  pm.test('Error message mentions SSRF or security', () => {",
                  "      const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "      const errorText = JSON.stringify(response).toLowerCase();",
                  "      pm.expect(errorText).to.satisfy((text) => {",
                  "          return text.includes('ssrf') || ",
                  "                 text.includes('blocked') || ",
                  "                 text.includes('private') ||",
                  "                 text.includes('security');",
                  "      });",
                  "  });",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"source_url\": \"http://192.168.1.1/video.mp4\",\n  \"target_privacy\": \"private\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/videos/imports",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "videos",
                "imports"
              ]
            }
          }
        },
